IF ccr_thdoc_d is MF 1 AND ccr_estriol_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_thaldo_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 0 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
